></span></strong>，據聞亦只有哥本哈根機場免稅店，及國內極少數超市找到。我們於丹麥頭進行街訪，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幾乎所有當地人都不認識此品牌。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d68dca1a4f4680f2149e9cca3347dffbd82eea31","tid":558440,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66a69e2f608ef5941c8a9ba7b3f69279bd8d0c9d","tid":558440,"uid":93479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:57:44.000Z","msg":"我畀德國寶呃撚左十幾年<br />\n細細個真以為係德國造<br />\n屌佢老母鬼鬼鼠鼠又告唔撚到佢商品說明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:29:13.000Z","msg":"用人地枝國旗，其實有冇問題"},{"pid":"a1fc61a7750fa767b4a5ab7fd11c899ee3bb761e","tid":558440,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb22dad8671e8c7e3f42832dd967d711e123f0f2","tid":558440,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3811b422da9902d810ce15cbf07d1c1236a2d650","tid":558440,"uid":693,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0cb51f4c6dde9dd717e87d0e207e30154037f30f","tid":558440,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:17:25.000Z","msg":"「丹麥」藍罐曲奇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"呢個真係丹麥整喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"丹麥人十個九個都未聽過自己有藍罐曲奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;現在一街都見到丹麥曲奇，其實真正在丹麥做的不多，大部份於亞洲製造，卻放上丹麥的圖片、文字　甚至國旗魚目混珠。「它們根本做不到聲稱的標準，牛油成份、口味、有些更用防腐劑及人造色素。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/travel/daily/article/20180212/20300569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftravel%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180212%2F20300569&d=mG%2FCcgV8bzEAAY37QBwOIcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0eb7c00b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2F